message: Clarify that orchestra does not pollute your $HOME

Updated rev.ng developers bootstrap guide

It is no longer recommended to add personal remotes to orchestra
configuration and instead developers are encouraged to manually add
their remotes to the specific repositories they want to fork.

README.md: reorder the steps in `Bootstrap`

Reorder the steps in `Bootstrap` to avoid missing packages (such as
`graphviz`, `graphviz-dev`, etc.) on a naked Ubuntu.
